Title: xXx: The Return of Xander Cage Official Trailer #1 (2017) Vin Diesel Action Movie HD
Comment:
Honestly it looks like a lot of dumb fun which is what i considered the last two, but it also feels like Vin Diesel must be putting his input into the films he works on because all the movies he's in are starting to bleed together stylistically and i'm starting to feel a strange sense of deja vu every time one of his films come to my attention. 

What with the same worn out tropes/cliches and cringe inducing dialog where everyone is an untouchable badass until the end of the movie, supporting no actual emotional weight, coupled with CGI distractions and orchestral flourishes to trick us into thinking what watched had some heart to it.

I'm going to see it, but I have the strangest feeling that the best stuff was in the trailer and even if that isn't the case, I'm fearful that most of it will be incredible stock and standard action movie tropes that dummies will devour with smiles.

Bollywood actor Deepika Padukone made her Hollywood debut with this film. Reportedly she had earlier turned down an offer to work on Furious 7 (2015) after unavailability of dates.

Donnie Yen replaced Jet Li for the role of Xiang after Li dropped out for undisclosed reasons.

Michael Bisping replaced Conor McGregor after McGregor pulled out. Both are UFC champion in their respected weight class.

This marks the second incident where Vin Diesel opted out of the second entry of a series that he originally launched as the lead before reprising the role again. Diesel also skipped the second entry of The Fast and the Furious series.
